        "old_string": "/**\n * TaskFlow Pro — A task and order management system.\n *\n * Architecture:\n * - Service Layer: UserService, OrderService, NotificationService (business logic)\n * - Repository Layer: UserRepository, OrderRepository (data access via Repository pattern)\n * - Adapter Layer: EmailAdapter, SmsAdapter (notification delivery channels)\n * - Utility Layer: Database, Logger, Pagination (infrastructure)\n * - Event System: EventBus with typed events (decoupled communication)\n *\n * Key architectural decisions:\n * 1. Repository pattern for all data access (no direct DB calls from services)\n * 2. Event-driven notifications — ALL inter-service communication goes through EventBus\n * 3. Adapter pattern for notification delivery — all channels implement NotificationAdapter\n */",
        "new_string": "/**\n * TaskFlow Pro — A task and order management system.\n *\n * Architecture:\n * - Service Layer: UserService, OrderService, NotificationService, PreferencesService, NotificationHistoryService\n * - Repository Layer: UserRepository, OrderRepository, PreferencesRepository, NotificationLogRepository\n * - Adapter Layer: EmailAdapter, SmsAdapter, WebhookAdapter (notification delivery channels)\n * - Validator Layer: UserValidator, OrderValidator, PreferencesValidator (pure validation functions)\n * - Utility Layer: Database, Logger, Pagination (infrastructure)\n * - Event System: EventBus with typed events (decoupled communication)\n *\n * Key architectural decisions:\n * 1. Repository pattern for all data access (no direct DB calls from services)\n * 2. Event-driven notifications — ALL inter-service communication goes through EventBus\n * 3. Adapter pattern for notification delivery — all channels implement NotificationAdapter\n * 4. Multi-channel preferences — email (opt-out), SMS (opt-in), webhook (opt-in)\n * 5. Append-only notification history via event-driven logging\n */"
      },
